data.description: Welcome to country living in this charming, updated farmhouse in northern Springfield! This home features 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and is a perfect blend of cozy living spaces and contemporary amenities. Beautiful, original wood floors throughout, including under the living room carpet. The large kitchen with stainless steal appliances is open to the dining room, perfect for entertaining! Upstairs you'll find 3 bedrooms and an updated bathroom. The full, unfinished basement offers plenty of storage. Situated on a spacious 1-acre lot, this property offers a generous fenced-in yard, providing a secure haven for both pets and children to play freely. Out front there's a concrete pad that can be used with a basketball hoop or set up a sitting area to enjoy your morning coffee! Convenient location to schools, highway, shopping and more! New cistern and water filtration system, 2023.
